Task -1

public class Student {

	@Id
	@Column(name="roll_number")
	private int rollNumber;
	
	@Column(name="student_name")
	private String studentName;
	
	@Column(name="email")
	private String email;
	
	@Column(name="mark")
	private BigDecimal mark;
	
}
public class Teacher{
	
	@Id
	@Column(name="teacher_id")
	Integer teacherId;
	
	@Column(name="teacher_name")
	private String teacherName;
	
	@Column(name="department")
	private String department;
	
	@OneToMany(targetEntity = Student.class,fetch = FetchType.EAGER,cascade = CascadeType.ALL)
	@JoinColumn(name = "teacher_ref", referencedColumnName = "teacher_id")
	Set<Student> students;
	
	
}

For the Entity given above create a JPA Repository Based CRUD Application
Add the Following method to the repository and provide endpoints to access them
Provide a method to find the students of a given department
Find the average mark of students a given department
Add the Open API Documentation 
ADD the Actuator Info endpoint
Secure the controller endpoints with in-memory Database
Optionally  use profiles to configure


